        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Sloth Of The Security",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128909237654",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository f9ddce50-b7e7-4411-a3eb-c2f908dc0abb).Image",
        "Description": "Your name is Phineas Whitmer, private detective. You have been contracted to solve a murder mystery and have noticed multiple ways to get into the building unnoticed. Punish the sin of sloth by retiring the security guards assigned to the points with an item near the entrance point itself. As the holes in the security are so gaping, it would be best to complete this mission entirely in your suit, however entering undercover would be satisfactory.",
